title: Darkside
description:
The Krainian Empire has invaded the outer territories! Take the
controls of the ArkLight X-52 and blast your way through hundreds
of massive, alien-packed asteroids in this pulse-pounding sci-fi
shoot em up!

Full Version Advantages:

Unlimited, unrestricted gameplay.
Complete hundreds of fast paced levels.
Play 3 game modes including Arcade.
Collect 10 power ups of mass destruction.
Fly through massive 3D asteroids.

System Requirements:

Windows 2000; Windows Vista; Windows XP
Graphics Card 3D video card (32 MB)
DirectX Version DirectX 8.1
Processor Speed (MHz)
HD Space (GB)
RAM (MB) 64
